(189, 'SLAITO Member area changes', 'SLAITO WEB - Members Area – 29 Aug 25 \r\n\r\n-	User Management \r\no	Admin Access\r\n	Ability to reset password.\r\n	Ability to delete and change primary email \r\n	Ability to change content is not appropriate. \r\n\r\n\r\n-	Profile Details \r\no	Admin Access\r\n	The admin should create the member with the bellow details and a one-time use password. \r\n•	Company Name (As Per Business Registration) \r\n•	SLAITO Join Date \r\n•	SLAITO Membership Number \r\n•	Category of membership \r\n•	Number of PAX \r\n	Further to this. Admin should be able to see all the details of members in a table view and should be able to download the following \r\n•	All contact details in an XLSX/ CSV sorted per company \r\n•	All contact details in an XLSX/ CSV sorted per person \r\n•	Contact details for 1 company in a PDF.\r\n\r\no	Member Access \r\n	Each member should be able to update the following details, some of these details should be updated under the member page. \r\n•	Company Name (Display Name) – Shown on member page \r\n•	Company Name (As Per Business Registration) \r\n•	Company Description - 500–700 characters – Shown on member page\r\n•	Company General Email - Shown on member page\r\n•	Company Office Address - Shown on member page\r\n•	Company Website - Shown on member page\r\n•	Company Facebook - Shown on member page\r\n•	Company Instagram - Shown on member page\r\n•	Company LinkedIn - Shown on member page\r\n•	Main Office Number - Shown on member page\r\n•	Company Logo - Shown on member page\r\n•	Adding contact information, each company should be able to provide 3 of contact persons. Not shown on Member Pages \r\no	First Name \r\no	Last Name \r\no	Designation \r\no	Mobile (Whatsapp Number) \r\no	Email \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n-	Careers \r\no	Admin Access \r\n	The admin should be able to delete CV Postings by non-members & Job Postings from Members \r\no	Member Access\r\n	Should be able to post a job and under that job they should be able to receive CVs for the Job. \r\n	ONLY THE PARTICULAR MEMBER SHOULD GET THE CVs \r\n\r\n-	Content Hub\r\no	Admin Access \r\n	Learning Center & Reports – \r\n•	Admin should be able to post the re', 4, 4, 'completed', 'medium', '2025-10-31', '2025-10-22 03:43:55', '2025-10-24 09:50:51'),
