(322, 'AIC system changes', 'Exchange Rate Issue:\r\nExchange rates are not being saved and are not visible on the next payment approval page when selecting the same date. Kindly look into this.\r\n\r\nReceipt Display Format:\r\n\r\nIf a student has a due amount, only the due should be displayed.\r\n\r\nIf a student has an overpayment, the overpayment amount should be clearly shown.\r\n\r\nReceipt Layout Update:\r\nThe order of information in the receipt needs to be updated as per the attachment. Kindly amend accordingly.\r\n\r\nSave Function Behavior:\r\nAcross the portal, clicking the Save button redirects to the previous page. Once saved, the page should remain where the user is currently working. Please update this behavior.\r\n\r\nDemo Portal Integration:\r\nPlease integrate the demo portal into the live version for testing purposes, as the enrolled students are available only in the live system, making testing difficult.\r\n\r\nInstallment Adjustments (Important):\r\nWhen a student makes overpayment or partial/due payment, the system must automatically adjust the next installment amount accordingly.\r\n\r\nStudents should not have to calculate the balance manually.\r\n\r\nThis automation is essential for accuracy and convenience.', 10, 10, 'completed', 'medium', '2025-11-28', '2025-11-27 04:52:32', '2025-12-02 03:08:35'),
