(597, 'EXEL', '1.	The main banner timing should be adjusted, and the same web movement/animation used on the Emil website should be applied.\r\n2.	The “View Details” option should appear all the lines should be in one line , and the text should be top aligned.\r\n3.	Colour options should be applied to the filtering function.\r\n4.	The “Our Collection” text section should be removed.\r\n5.	Under Related Products, more items should be displayed in the same colour range, and additional products should appear when viewed on mobile devices.\r\n6.	‘Visit the Exel Holdings showroom to explore our collection and experience the beauty and quality of our products up close ” promotional message should be displayed on each page.\r\n7.	Provide colour tab options for the “View Details” section.\r\n8.	Adjust the image-to-text ratio to display larger images and less text.\r\n9.	The Downloads section should be updated.\r\n10.	Mosaic installation details should be included under the Mosaic and Services pages.\r\n11.	“Contact the Salesperson” option should appear on every product detail page, depending on the product.\r\n12.	Architect / Client names should appear on project images.\r\n13.	Laying patterns should be included on the Mosaic page, categorized supplier-wise.', 9, 9, 'completed', 'medium', '2026-03-17', '2026-03-09 12:56:57', '2026-03-23 06:10:52'),
