(764, 'Animal Health Production', 'Employee Management\r\n\r\n•	Employee management activities completed as planned.\r\n\r\nAdvance Programmes (To-Do List) / Diaries Management\r\n\r\n•	Daily tasks maintained (Date, Place, Activity, Priority)\r\n•	Advanced programmes updated\r\n•	Annual Performance Plan prepared for the upcoming year\r\n\r\nLeave Management\r\n\r\n•	Functionality implemented to maintain Casual, Sick, Foreign, Maternity, and Annual leave records of all employees.\r\n•	The Leave Management section is now functioning after completion of the Employee user role setup.\r\n\r\nInquiry Management\r\n\r\n•	Recording inquiries received\r\n•	Forwarding inquiries to relevant units\r\n•	Maintaining inquiry tracking records\r\n\r\nRight to Information Activities\r\n\r\n•	Section structure prepared as per requirement\r\n', 9, 9, 'completed', 'medium', '2026-07-17', '2026-07-17 06:43:22', '2026-07-17 06:50:31'),
