(768, 'Animal Health Production', '1. Employee Profile Management\r\nEmployees are now provided with secure access to their personalized profiles, where they can view their details along with system verification status. Kindly review the current structure and confirm so we can proceed with finalizing the functional profile setup.\r\n2. Daily Tasks & Diary Hub\r\nA comprehensive module has been implemented to support daily activity tracking:\r\n•	Recording Engine: Enables employees to log their daily tasks with key details such as Date, Place, Activity, and Priority levels.\r\n•	Live Ledger: Includes a dynamic and searchable data table, allowing users to easily review past records, with additional export options (CSV, Excel, and Print) for reporting and documentation purposes.\r\n3. Leave Management System\r\nThe leave management functionality has been designed to handle multiple request types and streamline tracking:\r\n•	Multi-Type Requests: Employees can apply for various leave categories including Casual (24), Sick (24), Foreign, Duty, and Maternity leave.\r\n•	Tracking & History: Provides real-time visibility into request statuses (Pending, Approved, Rejected), along with a complete history of submitted requests for transparency and record-keeping.\r\n', 9, 9, 'completed', 'medium', '2026-07-17', '2026-07-17 06:44:05', '2026-07-17 06:53:10');
