(941, 'Gem and Jewellery Website', 'Diploma in Gemmology and Jewellery – Payment Structure Update\r\n\r\nThe payment structure for the Diploma in Gemmology and Jewellery should be updated as follows:\r\n\r\nDiploma in Gemmology\r\n\r\n* Course Fee: Rs. 200,000.00\r\n* Registration Fee: Rs. 5,000.00\r\n* Refundable Deposit: Rs. 5,000.00\r\n\r\nWhen a user clicks on the Diploma in Gemmology course, the total payable amount displayed should be Rs. 210,000.00.\r\n\r\nThe first payment should consist of: ( Half of the course fee, Registration fee and  Refundable deposit)\r\n\r\nTotal First Payment: Rs. 110,000.00\r\n(Calculated as: 100,000 + 5,000 + 5,000)\r\n\r\nDiploma in Jewellery\r\n\r\n* Course Fee: Rs. 125,000.00\r\n* Registration Fee: Rs. 2,500.00\r\n* Refundable Deposit: Rs. 5,000.00\r\n\r\nWhen a user clicks on the Diploma in Jewellery course, the total payable amount displayed should be Rs. 132,500.00.\r\n\r\nThe first payment should consist of: ( Half of the course fee, Registration fee and Refundable deposit)\r\n\r\nTotal First Payment: Rs. 70,000.00\r\n(Calculated as: 62,500 + 2,500 + 5,000)', 9, 9, 'completed', 'medium', '2026-07-22', '2026-07-22 12:17:50', '2026-07-23 04:38:27'),
(942, 'Teeda meeting', 'meeting at 11AM ', 10, 10, 'pending', 'medium', '2026-07-23', '2026-07-22 12:50:15', '2026-07-22 12:50:15'),
