(944, 'Meeting with Chief Justice – Progress Review of Civil Appeal HC, Commercial HC, Criminal HC, Colombo DC & Colombo MC', 'Conduct a progress review meeting with the Chief Justice (CJ) to present the current development status of the following court systems:\r\n\r\nCivil Appeal High Court\r\nCommercial High Court\r\nCriminal High Court\r\nColombo District Court (DC)\r\nColombo Magistrate Court (MC)\r\n\r\nDiscussion Points -\r\n\r\nPresent the current progress of each website and Case Management System (CMS).\r\nDemonstrate completed features and recently implemented functionalities.\r\nHighlight ongoing developments and pending tasks.\r\nDiscuss issues, challenges, and dependencies affecting progress.\r\nGather feedback, recommendations, and approvals from the Chief Justice.\r\nRecord action items and follow-up tasks based on the meeting outcomes.', 4, 4, 'completed', 'high', '2026-07-23', '2026-07-23 04:53:41', '2026-07-23 04:53:55'),
